  "about_item": [
    "🐾【2-in-1 Dog Crate Furniture | Stylish & Multifunctional】This dog crate doubles as a sleek end table, blending seamlessly with home decor. It works as functional furniture while serving as a secure pet crate, adding a decorative touch and saving space. A tasteful balance of utility and style for any home.",
    "🐾【Spacious for Small Dogs | Secure Lockable Door】Measuring 29.5\"L x 21\"W x 25.2\"H, it offers ample space for small dogs to lounge comfortably. Equipped with a secure lockable door, it prevents escapes and keeps your pup safe when you’re away. Ideal for daily indoor and outdoor use.",
    "🐾【Chew-Resistant Plastic | Safe & Durable】Crafted from high-quality safe plastic, this heavy-duty dog kennel resists daily wear. Its chew-resistant surface stands up to energetic pups’ biting and scratching, ensuring long-term durability. A safe choice for your furry friend.",
    "🐾【Tool-Free Assembly | Quick & Hassle-Free】Assembly is hassle-free even for beginners, with clearly labeled parts and detailed instructions. No special tools or experience needed—finish putting this pet crate together in minutes and use it right away.",
    "🐾【Easy-to-Clean Design | Low-Maintenance】The smooth plastic surface resists dirt, stains and pet odors for easy cleaning. Simply wipe with a damp cloth or mild cleaner to restore its fresh look. No tedious scrubbing, saving you time and effort."
  ],
